Transcription.Text: Having exhausted their invention in the preparation of stimulants for the palate, they broke fresh ground and called another sense to their aid. By delicate application of odours and richly-distilled perfumes, these refined voluptuaries aroused the fainting appetite and added a more exquisite and ethereal enjoyment to the grosser pleasures of the Board.
